import React, {useContext, useState} from 'react'; import './assets/css/about-me.css'; const AboutMe = () => { return (

Joseph Bautista

Software Developer

Hi, I am a software developer based in the Philippines. I have more than 5 years working in software development industry. I worked as Full Stack Web Application Developer for more than 4 years and, right now, I am working as Back End Engineer at Xctuality Lte. Ptd., a Singapore-based tech-start up, for more than a year until present. I believe that studying is a lifetime commitment, that's why during my free time I am exploring new things in tech such as blockchain technology, cryptocurrency and Artificial Intelligence.

I am open for new opportunities that would need my services in software development. If you have one for me, please email me at josephreuben.bautista@gmail.com

I am looking forward to work with you. Kudos!

); }; export default AboutMe;
